column3: Looking at the output in `bitcoin_config.h` PACKAGE_VERSION is defined in the same way so there should be no user-visible change. I cannot find it being defined anywhere (at a higher level) so I suppose it's part of the autoconf system.\n\nCode review ACK f12fbad5a1852706184082c68655fafad4bb9fe1
